The Lead_Invocable_Update_State_based_on_Area_Code-8 invocable process failed to start because a valid value wasn't found. This can happen when entities that invoke Lead_Invocable_Update_State_based_on_Area_Code-8, such as other processes, don't have values for either the SObject or SObjectId. For example: -An SObject or SObject ID wasn't specified. -A value might have been included, but it was null at runtime.
